datasets.name: hpx_homepage_summary_dataset
queryLines: SELECT home_tile, SUM(unique_tile_views) as total_unique_tile_views, SUM(unique_tile_clicks) as total_unique_tile_clicks, SUM(unique_interstitial_views) as total_unique_interstitial_views, SUM(unique_interstitial_primary_button_clicks) as total_unique_interstitial_primary_button_clicks, SUM(unique_interstitial_secondary_button_clicks) as total_unique_interstitial_secondary_button_clicks, AVG(home_tile_clicked_vs_homepage_displayed) as avg_home_tile_clicked_vs_homepage_displayed, AVG(primary_button_clicked_vs_tile_displayed) as avg_primary_button_clicked_vs_tile_displayed, AVG(secondary_button_clicked_vs_tile_displayed) as avg_secondary_button_clicked_vs_tile_displayed, AVG(primary_button_clicked_vs_interstitial_displayed) as avg_primary_button_clicked_vs_interstitial_displayed, AVG(secondary_button_clicked_vs_interstitial_displayed) as avg_secondary_button_clicked_vs_interstitial_displayed FROM team_css_analytics_prod.hpx_analytics.hpx_events_model_homepage_summary_metric_view GROUP BY home_tile ORDER BY total_unique_tile_views DESC
